name: I Fed Them With Alien
description:
Made during the Game Jam Zurich Milan 2015, organized by Ludicious – Zurich Game Festival & Playing The Game.

More info here:
→ Game Jam Zurich Milan, a memorable experience
→ Game Conference Zurich Milan, our Game Jam at the Expo 2015

Move your character with W-A-S-D keys and leave the food with M and N.
